{"tid":975402,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"隻poodle 最近幾篤屎都係咁，求救","createTime":"2019-01-09T15:07:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T03:01:47.000Z","uid":28150,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9a88faf9c1c4ac82d66190a9705b4f01223ce7bd","tid":975402,"uid":28150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mXqet4y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmXqet4y.png&h=e1816ece&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一次養狗，依兩日隻狗屙啲屎都係咁，中間黑黑紅紅，點解會咁？ 佢其他野又好正常喎，食得訓得玩得。再係咁聽日帶佢睇醫生"},{"pid":"fd2b0b3c29b44619b02869932d02007dfd3721f2","tid":975402,"uid":28150,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k2nMkdk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk2nMkdk.png&h=f555285a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n擔心死我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132a71e441ebe87b7949978767137af26ff558e8","tid":975402,"uid":59015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無食啲乜野？ 有無做趴低前身既姿勢？"},{"pid":"3e80810411d1ef1c0f7b9c2a998362a07643c66b","tid":975402,"uid":21757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:32:12.000Z","msg":"有冇杜蟲"},{"pid":"b7832032952d3018dac83fb796ed0de680e21519","tid":975402,"uid":71133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:32:48.000Z","msg":"似有蟲"},{"pid":"29379886dec63da71e609e8f63ab263e74e6ec99","tid":975402,"uid":89665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:34:03.000Z","msg":"食杜蟲"},{"pid":"9879ea78e6dd8dfe941008a966fa41b83350a3b9","tid":975402,"uid":40812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim