樓主帶佢睇完醫生請更新一下狀況。<br />\n<br />\n講開私人繁殖，之前fb group有人出post 搵狗捐血，隻狗又係上綱買，點知返屋企第二日就病到七彩入埋院。我隻狗剛好適合血型輸埋血，可惜最後救唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。睇住隻狗仔好辛苦，最後捱唔住走左真係好慘。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以真係唔好再幫襯私人繁殖場啦！<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"4479753a78d146cd0c0670fa5cdee21de9a9f0f0","tid":975402,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T01:42:22.000Z","msg":"狗主果然係自私撚 , 一入個post就見到屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3c06ce33f95eff14ceb0a44c12fe77bddab1ae","tid":975402,"uid":33632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"132a71e441ebe87b7949978767137af26ff558e8","tid":975402,"uid":59015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無食啲乜野？ 有無做趴低前身既姿勢？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:03:06.000Z","msg":"趴低前身係咪姐係兩隻手伸向前 心口貼地 後腳伸直 patpat &quot;趷&quot; 高？<br />\n<br />\n想問下呢個姿勢係咪有問題<br />\n<br />\n因為我隻史納莎都有做過呢個動作 見過幾次"},{"pid":"0e6ffd76cf0bffbf5718ef48e2d4a5eae73c396c","tid":975402,"uid":59015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e3c06ce33f95eff14ceb0a44c12fe77bddab1ae","tid":975402,"uid":33632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"132a71e441ebe87b7949978767137af26ff558e8","tid":975402,"uid":59015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無食啲乜野？ 有無做趴低前身既姿勢？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:03:06.000Z","msg":"趴低前身係咪姐係兩隻手伸向前 心口貼地 後腳伸直 patpat &quot;趷&quot; 高？<br />\n<br />\n想問下呢個姿勢係咪有問題<br />\n<br />\n因為我隻史納莎都有做過呢個動作 見過幾次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:14:19.000Z","msg":"肚唔舒服會hold 住呢個動作， <br />\n亦可能只係伸懶腰 or 佢本身鍾意做呢個動作，要睇埋有無其他唔妥"},{"pid":"64e00bf9268e4fd9b06e7bde513454d7b91dab2b","ti